@@@ MIGRATIONS
============
---To add migrations  
   =>dotnet ef migrations add ActivityAttendee -p Persistence -s API
       -p == project name -s == start up project 
---to remove migrations  => dotnet ef migrations remove  


1--dotnet new list   ---to see all .net projects
